          },
          "reviewBody": "I feel proud to be a part of this wonderful institution. My school is not just a place of education; it is a second home where dreams are nurtured and futures are shaped.\nApart from academics, my school gives equal importance to sports, cultural activities, and competitions. Various events, celebrations, and educational trips are organized throughout the year, which help students explore their talents and build confidence.\nThe discipline system of the school is excellent. It teaches us punctuality, respect, teamwork, and responsibility. The principal and management are dedicated and always strive to provide the best opportunities for students.\nThe teachers are highly supportive, caring, and always ready to guide us not only in academics but also in life values. They explain every concept clearly and encourage us to ask questions without hesitation.",
