            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "\"God's Grace School is an exceptional institution that nurtures young minds in a supportive and inclusive environment.\n\nThe dedicated faculty, cutting-edge facilities, and comprehensive curriculum make it an ideal place for students to grow academically, socially, and spiritually. The school's emphasis on character development, critical thinking, and innovation equips students with skills to excel in an ever-changing world.\n\nI highly recommend God's Grace School to parents seeking a well-rounded education for their children. The school's commitment to excellence shines through in every aspect, making it a truly exceptional learning experience.\"\n\n\"God's Grace School offers a world-class education with caring teachers, state-of-the-art facilities, and a focus on character development.\n\nHighly recommend!\"",
