          "reviewBody": "God's Grace School, Barrackpore: Providing a solid academic and moral basis for developing minds.\nExcellent teachers, helpful positive environment.\nThey place a strong emphasis on extracurricular activities and academics as part of their holistic development model. A strong focus on essential subjects, pupils who are ready for a higher education.\n\nInspired by God's Grace Academy Barrackpore\n\nStrongly advised!",
