            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am absolutely delighted with the education and experience provided by this school.\nit's been incredible to see my brother thrive in such a supportive and stimulating environment. The teachers are truly exceptional - knowledgeable, passionate, and dedicated to helping each student reach their full potential.\n\nThe curriculum is well-rounded and engaging, with a perfect balance of academics, arts, and extracurricular activities.\n\nThe facilities are modern and well-maintained, providing a comfortable and safe space for learning and growth.\n\nCommunication between teachers, administrators, and parents is seamless, ensuring that everyone is always on the same page.\n\nI couldn't be more grateful for the opportunity to be a part of this community and I highly recommend this school to anyone seeking an exceptional education for their child.",
